<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef9121df-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s103503"><num value="103503">§ 103503.</num><heading> Summary to Congress</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall provide with the submission of the President’s annual budget a summary of the status and funding of signature projects and programs.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef9121e0-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/114/289/tI/s101/a">Pub. L. 114–289, title I, § 101(a)</ref>, <date date="2016-12-16">Dec. 16, 2016</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/130/1484">130 Stat. 1484</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
